ttsdata.text: What do you mean you lost your job?
It's not my fault, a virus somehow got on my computer!
I don't care if it wasn't your fault! How are we going to afford to live!
I don't know.
I'll meet you at the park.
Who are you talking to?
Um...Gilbert?
Oh yeah, that reminds me, I'm selling Gilbert!
No, you can't do that!
Sorry, we can't afford to raise him.
Great, now the living room is destroyed!
Now the cat's got to go!
Get back here!
I hope someone online can help me.
Who could that be?
Hello, I have heard you have a financial problem on your hands!
Ew, a business friendly character.
Whoa there, let's not be racist.
Alright, come inside.
So, who are you and why are you here?
My name is jack Paul, and I have a solution to all your financial problems!
What is it?
All you have to do is sign this contract!
Alright.
Thank you.
